    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a mechanic's project or as a donor for parts. The engine requires significant work to be reliably roadworthy, and the transmission shifts harshly. Cosmetically, there is extensive rust on the wheel arches and undercarriage, along with multiple deep scratches and fading paint throughout. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold as-is, and towing is recommended.",
