    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with that new-car scent and absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standards. For a buyer seeking a collector-grade example that requires zero investment, this is the ideal choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
