      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent maintenance history and robust mechanical performance. The exterior retains a professional finish, complemented by an interior environment that has been preserved with care. This unit has undergone a rigorous assessment to ensure it meets our standards for safety and operational efficiency. It represents a premier opportunity for an owner seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 31500.0,
